OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy low cloud will linger at
OL,6,Ffirst across the region, but skies
OL,7,Fwill gradually brighten through the
OL,8,Fmorning. Some very warm and hazy
OL,9,Fspells of sunshine will develop with
OL,10,Flight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAfter a bright and warm
OL,13,Fevening, low cloud will move back in
OL,14,Fovernight to bring mist and fog
OL,15,Fpatches in some areas. Staying dry and
OL,16,Fwarm overnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FLow cloud will burn back
OL,19,Fduring the morning to bring sunny
OL,20,Fskies. Feeling very warm in the
OL,21,Fsunshine and light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
