OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FStaying dry and increasingly hot
OL,7,Fthrough the outlook. Plenty of strong
OL,8,Fsunshine and light winds, with some
OL,9,Fwarm nights too.
